{"tid":760362,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[街機]EXVSMBON跟機一問","createTime":"2018-07-29T12:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T18:39:44.000Z","uid":63843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7e48848de1482c724b0ebafd87fab1fab162c879","tid":760362,"uid":63843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T12:39:08.000Z","msg":"今日同朋友4個人圍內打shuffle 2v2<br />\n有條友望左我地4條友一陣先1蚊跟機<br />\n但係問題係 shuffle機唔齊4個會係各自各單機打電腦 冇4個人入錢既話係打唔到2v2<br />\n<br />\n姐係條友跟完機淨係可以打單機mode<br />\n亦都冇任何人去第4個位入錢<br />\n<br />\n但附近亦都有成十幾部機係有位 <br />\n有幾組4連機都有位 唔會阻到人<br />\n想打單機唔洗跟 直接坐低入錢就得<br />\n<br />\n最後我地4個換左位去隔離既shuffle 2v2繼續打<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問下除左佢格硬想阻住我地圍內打之外<br />\n佢咁做有咩目的??<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728d6cc4913de48601923de51a43efad0bdc4daa","tid":760362,"uid":63843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T12:44:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72784751fe53fde1614dee0f61147ce51f12ece0","tid":760362,"uid":63843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T12:48:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d6a3e5cd1c402e5d86a859ed71be33187d6a68","tid":760362,"uid":33696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T12:49:33.000Z","msg":"試過啦<br />\n成日俾銀牌挑機<br />\n<br />\n試過為左唔俾外人跟機<br />\n約班fd星期六9點鐘係新知門口捕開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8844539f8ae25654701c124e1922fac9b81b736","tid":760362,"uid":63843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51d6a3e5cd1c402e5d86a859ed71be33187d6a68","tid":760362,"uid":33696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T12:49:33.000Z","msg":"試過啦<br />\n成日俾銀牌挑機<br />\n<br />\n試過為左唔俾外人跟機<br />\n約班fd星期六9點鐘係新知門口捕開門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cit